---
title:   'UI Kit'
section: 'ui-kit'
slug:    'ui-kit'
---

- content_for :header do
  %header.aptible-header.hero-gradient--angled
    = partial 'partials/main-nav'
    .about-heading.heading--single-center.heading--condensed
      %h1.heading__title.heading__title--no-hr.heading__title--centered
        Aptible Marketing UI Kit
      %p.heading__summary--single-center.heading__summary--light-blue-gray
        Components and documentation for building marketing pages

.content
  .grid-container
    .grid-item
      %h3 Checbox

      .custom-checkbox
        %input#request-demo-of{ type: 'checkbox' }
        %label{ for: 'request-demo-of' }
          = partial '/images/icons/checkbox.svg'
          I would like to schedule a demo.

  .grid-container
    .grid-item
      %h3 Enclave Carousel
      = partial 'enclave/carousel'

  .grid-container
    .grid-item
      %h3 Terminal
      .terminal__title Your Healthco Terminal
      %pre.highlight.plaintext
        %table.rouge-table.rouge-table--with-title
          %tr
            %td.rouge-code.rouge-code--no-num.rouge-code--terminal
              .terminal $ aptible login
              .terminal-interactive Email: osvaldo@aptible.com
              .terminal-interactive Password:
              .terminal-interactive 2FA Token: 555999
              .terminal-response Success! Token written to $HOME/.aptible/tokens.json


.content.aptible-header--bottom-grid.angled-section-divider__mask
  .grid-container
    .grid-item
      %h3 Angled Divider

.content.hero-gradient-with-dividers--dark
  .grid-container
    .grid-item.hero.text-center
      %h3.subtitle--caps
        Enclave automates security controls
      %h2.title.title--white
        Container Orchestration and DevOps Automation
      %h3.subtitle
        Enclave helps you automate your DevOps work as it implements the
        security controls you need to deploy in regulated industries

.content
  .grid-container
    .grid-item.hero.text-center.hero--dark
      %h2.title
        Container Orchestration and DevOps Automation
      %h2.subtitle
        Enclave helps you automate your DevOps work as it implements the
        security controls you need to deploy in regulated industries

  .grid-container
    .grid-item
      %h2.title Buttons
      %a.btn{:href => ""} Link Button
      %button Button
      %input{:type => "submit", :value => "Submit Button"}/
      %input.btn--outline{:type => "submit", :value => "Submit Button"}/

.content
  .grid-container
    .text-center.hero--dark
      %h2.title Image Cards

    .grid--3up-flex
      .grid-item.img-card
        .img-card__image
          = partial '/images/12-factors.svg'
        .img-card__title
          Twelve-Factor App Deployment
        .img-card__copy
          Enclave is a mature, twelve-factor app deployment platform, with
          security and compliance features built-in. It will fit right in with
          your existing developer workflow.
        .img-card__link
          %a.arrow-link--right.dbl-arrow-link--right{ href: '#' }
            What's a Twelve-Factor App?

      .grid-item.img-card
        .img-card__image
          = partial '/images/enclave-docker.svg'
        .img-card__title
          Platform as a Service for Dockerized Apps
        .img-card__copy
          Enclave provisions a VPC on your behalf and hosts your Docker
          containers and databases within it. You can run any code on Enclave
          that runs inside a Docker container, the standard and most widely-used
          software container platform.
        .img-card__link
          %a.arrow-link--right.dbl-arrow-link--right{ href: '#' }
            Get Started with Docker for Regulated Industries

      .grid-item.img-card
        .img-card__image
          = partial '/images/compliance.svg'
        .img-card__title
          Automated Regulatory Compliance and Customer Audits
        .img-card__copy
          Deploying in regulated industries means your entire security and
          compliance program should be in place from day 1. Enclave
          automatically implements security controls including data encryption,
          backup and restore procedures, audit logging, and more, so you canpass
          regulatory and customer audits while you focus on building your app.
        .img-card__link
          %a.arrow-link--right.dbl-arrow-link--right{ href: '#' }
            See all of Enclaveâ€™s Security Controls

.comparison-table
  .comparison-table__header
    .comparison-option
      = partial '/images/aws-logo.svg'
      .comparison-option__title Deploy with AWS
    .comparison-option
      = partial '/partials/aptible-mark'
      .comparison-option__title Deploy with Enclave

  .comparison-feature
    .comparison-feature__title Access Controls
    .comparison-feature__body
      .comparison-feature__point Select, implement, and maintain IAM Roles
      .comparison-feature__vs vs
      .comparison-feature__point Clear, maintainable role-based access controls

  .comparison-feature
    .comparison-feature__title Network Security & Load Balancing
    .comparison-feature__body
      .comparison-feature__point
        Configure and maintain instance and database security groups, provision
        SSL termination and orchestrate load balancing
      .comparison-feature__vs vs
      .comparison-feature__point
        %span.comparison-feature__automated Automated
        configuration and maintenance<br>(including SSL termination and load
        balancing)
